<!DOCTYPE html>
<html dir="rtl" lang="ar">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>معلومات الحساب</title>
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e293b 0%, #0f172a 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 2rem;
            color: #e2e8f0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .profile-header {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            animation: slideDown 0.5s ease-out;
        }

        .user-info {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .avatar {
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            background: #3b82f6;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            animation: pulse 2s infinite;
        }

        .user-details h1 {
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
        }

        .email {
            color: #94a3b8;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        .stats-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 1.5rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }

        .stat-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
            animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease-out;
        }

        .stat-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }

        .stat-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .stat-icon {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2);
            border-radius: 10px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: #3b82f6;
        }

        .stat-value {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 0.5rem 0;
        }

        .status {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .status-active {
            background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.2);
            color: #22c55e;
        }

        .status-blocked {
            background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.2);
            color: #ef4444;
        }

        .status-locked {
            background: rgba(234, 179, 8, 0.2);
            color: #eab308;
        }

        .tokens-list {
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }

        .token-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            animation: slideUp 0.5s ease-out;
        }

        .token-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .token-info {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
            color: #94a3b8;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .progress-bar {
            width: 100%;
            height: 6px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 3px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .progress-fill {
            height: 100%;
            background: #3b82f6;
            border-radius: 3px;
            animation: progressFill 2s ease-out;
        }

        .countdown {
            font-family: monospace;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #ef4444;
            animation: blink 1s infinite;
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0% {
                box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.4);
            }
            70% {
                box-shadow: 0 0 0 20px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0);
            }
            100% {
                box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(59, 130, 246, 0);
            }
        }

        @keyframes slideDown {
            from {
                transform: translateY(-20px);
                opacity: 0;
            }
            to {
                transform: translateY(0);
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }

        @keyframes slideUp {
            from {
                transform: translateY(20px);
                opacity: 0;
            }
            to {
                transform: translateY(0);
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }

        @keyframes progressFill {
            from {
                width: 0;
            }
        }

        @keyframes blink {
            50% {
                opacity: 0.5;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .user-info {
                flex-direction: column;
                text-align: center;
            }

            .token-header {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 1rem;
            }

            .token-info {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="profile-header">
            <div class="user-info">
                <div class="avatar">
                    <i class="fas fa-user"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="user-details">
                    <h1>أحمد محمد</h1>
                    <div class="email">ahmed.mohamed@example.com</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="stats-grid">
            <div class="stat-card">
                <div class="stat-header">
                    <div class="stat-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-desktop"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>الأجهزة المسجلة</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-value">3 أجهزة</div>
                <div>آخر تسجيل دخول: قبل 2 ساعة</div>
            </div>

            <div class="stat-card">
                <div class="stat-header">
                    <div class="stat-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>حالة الحساب</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-value">
                    <span class="status status-locked">مقيد مؤقتاً لتسجيل الدخول</span>
                </div>
                <div>محاولات تسجيل دخول خاطئة متكررة</div>
                <div class="countdown">14:35 دقيقة متبقية</div>
            </div>

            <div class="stat-card">
                <div class="stat-header">
                    <div class="stat-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-key"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>محاولات تسجيل الدخول</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-value">5/5</div>
                <div>تم استنفاذ جميع المحاولات المسموحة</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tokens-list">
            <h2>الجلسات النشطة</h2>
            <div class="token-card">
                <div class="token-header">
                    <h3>Chrome - Windows 10</h3>
                    <div class="token-info">
                        <span><i class="fas fa-clock"></i> ينتهي في: 45 دقيقة</span>
                        <span><i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i> الرياض، المملكة العربية السعودية</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="progress-bar">
                    <div class="progress-fill" style="width: 25%"></div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="token-card">
                <div class="token-header">
                    <h3>iPhone 13 Pro</h3>
                    <div class="token-info">
                        <span><i class="fas fa-clock"></i> ينتهي في: 2 ساعة</span>
                        <span><i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i> الرياض، المملكة العربية السعودية</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="progress-bar">
                    <div class="progress-fill" style="width: 65%"></div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="token-card">
                <div class="token-header">
                    <h3>Firefox - MacBook Pro</h3>
                    <div class="token-info">
                        <span><i class="fas fa-clock"></i> ينتهي في: 3 ساعات</span>
                        <span><i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i> الرياض، المملكة العربية السعودية</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="progress-bar">
                    <div class="progress-fill" style="width: 85%"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>